'''Aḥwac''' (s [[Tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]] : ⴰⵃⵡⴰⵛ, s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]] : أحواش‎) iga yat [[Taẓuri tamaziɣt|taẓuri]], d yan anaw n umarg nna ittilin s trubbatin illa dar [[Imaziɣen|imaziɣn]] n iffus n [[Lmɣrib]] ma mu nttini [[iclḥiyn]] willi sawaln s [[Taclḥit|tclḥit]], iggut ɣ tmizar n [[Sus]] d [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|Waṭlas imẓẓiyn]] d way [[Aṭlas mqqurn|mqqurn]], tkraygat tamazirt nɣ adɣar ittuyssan s wanaw uḥwac lli sis iẓlin. Tmun tẓuẓi yad d imasn n umarg d iwaliwn. ilin gisn inawn ggutnin.<ref>https://sudstmaruc.cum/ahwach-la-traditiun-amaziɣ-du-maruc/</ref> 

Aḥwac ur igi ɣar yan urkkz unzil, ntta iga udm aḍnin n tudrt nna-d issnkarn asnflul d tmdyazt d ummutr ɣ ufulki, iga yat twlaft iddrn ar-d trara amrara n ufgan amaziɣ d akaraw nns agaman d anfgan ɣ umrara d issufuɣn inzgumn nɣd inaruzn nɣd tufrayin d timmutrin d tiwlafin ɣ umarur irar-tnt s tɣarast n usnflul s tiwlafin n tẓuri ifulkin. 

Ɣ uynnaɣ n umssugr amgraw, nna ɣ tswiri dis tagrawt tudrt nns tamktayt d amnlli, ɣ ammas n timyurin tiẓuriwin tidlsanin, nttat iɣ nra tga tamddit taẓawant turkkizt d anmiggir ismunun iẓuran n umsasa d idammn d tiddra, ɣ yan ummak amgraw imann, d iga yat tinml tanamunt ɣ tlla twizi ɣ tayri izddign ar tsxitir afrak anamun dar ifganen s izrfan nnsn d imafllaɣn-nnsn f unamur, d gratsn, ɣ uyddaɣ ttinin imdyazn n imukrisn d iswingimn ɣ yan ummak anamun ifulkin iɣudan s timyuriwin tiqburin tizaykutn.

Aḥwac tga yat tguri da twanna i-ku anawn n urkkz anamun. Mk-nna gan-t talɣiwin d inyatn nns ɣ iffus n [[Lmɣrib]] ɣ tasgiwin n [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|Waṭlas imẓẓiyn]] d itsn-t ɣ [[Aṭlas mqqurn|Waṭlas imqqurn]] d inna ɣ llan-t tiqbilin timaziɣin isawal-n s tutlayt [[taclḥit]]. Anamk-nns: amun n imzdaɣ n tmazirt ɣ yan udɣar iga s yism "Asays" nɣd "Asrir" nɣd "Asarag", afad ad ḥucn, ɣ yat tmddit taẓurant innurẓmn i-ku yan wanna iran ad idru s tguri nɣd tizlit nɣd anya.

Aḥwac tga yat trkkzt tanamunt ɣ ittdru ɣ tifri nns tarabbut n middn ur illi wattay nnsn, ilin-t ula tiwtmin, d iẓil ad gnt tifddamin macc tinna yuwln ur aɣ tdrunt macc irgazn ur gisn tlli tfada ad.

